OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772917927
OL,3,CInside Israel's offensive against
OL,4,CHezbollah on the Lebanese border
OL,6,FOver the past few days we've seen a
OL,7,Fmassive build-up of manpower and
OL,8,Ffirepower in Northern Israel.
OL,10,FAll day yesterday and again today,
OL,11,Fthere were tanks and personnel being
OL,12,Fsent to the Lebanese border for the
OL,13,FIDF's expanded offensive against
OL,14,FHezbollah.
OL,16,FThe Israeli military has moved into
OL,17,Fsouthern Lebanon with exceptional
OL,18,Fforce. But Hezbollah is not going down
OL,19,Fwithout a fight. Several times today,
OL,20,Fwe had to run for cover.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
