OL,3,CInside Israel's offensive against
OL,4,CHezbollah on the Lebanese border
OL,6,FIn Kfar Giladi, we met the Ze'evi
OL,7,Ffamily, who have lived in their
OL,8,Fvillage overlooking the beautiful Hula
OL,9,Fvalley for three generations.
OL,11,FNissan Ze'evi works as a first
OL,12,Fresponder. He was determined his wife
OL,13,Fand children would not be forced to
OL,14,Fevacuate during this war.
OL,16,FOn Friday afternoon, we filmed him and
OL,17,Fhis sons playing football on the
OL,18,Ffrontline.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772917927
OL,3,CInside Israel's offensive against
OL,4,CHezbollah on the Lebanese border
OL,6,FOn the hill above Nissan's house is a
OL,7,Fvillage which used to be a Hezbollah
OL,8,Fhideout. In the past the IDF razed it
OL,9,Fto the ground, and in that operation
OL,10,Fthey found not only a huge cache of
OL,11,Fweapons, but maps and plans indicating
OL,12,Fan infiltration like that seen on
OL,13,FOctober 7 was being planned.
OL,15,FThe ranks of Hezbollah have been
OL,16,Fdiminished in recent years as Israel
OL,17,Fhas targeted and eliminated many of
OL,18,Fits top officials, including leader
OL,19,FHassan Nasrallah.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772917927
OL,3,CInside Israel's offensive against
OL,4,CHezbollah on the Lebanese border
OL,6,FNissan echoed the sentiment of many
OL,7,Fwe've spoken to: That this could be an
OL,8,Fhistoric moment to wipe out the terror
OL,9,Fgroup once and for all.
OL,11,FA colonel from the 769 Brigade of
OL,12,FIsrael's Northern Command told me that
OL,13,Fthe operation could take days or
OL,14,Fweeks, but they are determined to
OL,15,Fbring it to that definitive conclusion.
OL,17,FThere have been gun fights, artillery
OL,18,Fexchanges and explosions from drones
OL,19,Fand missiles. Israel and Hezbollah are
OL,20,Ffighting with everything they've got.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
