PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772917927
OL,3,CInside Israel's offensive against
OL,4,CHezbollah on the Lebanese border
OL,6,FFor the Ze'evi family staying in their
OL,7,Fhome means spending a lot of time in
OL,8,Ftheir safe room. They have a bed and
OL,9,Fsupplies in their protected space,
OL,10,Fknowing sometimes it can take hours to
OL,11,Fget the all-clear.
OL,13,FI asked Nissan what he thought of
OL,14,Fyesterday's comments from Israel's
OL,15,FFinance Minister Bezalel Smotrich,
OL,16,Fwhen he threatened to turn Beirut into
OL,17,FKhan Younis, referring to the city in
OL,18,FGaza which has been destroyed in the
OL,19,Fwar there.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772917927
OL,3,CInside Israel's offensive against
OL,4,CHezbollah on the Lebanese border
OL,6,FNissan said if that's what it takes,
OL,7,Fthen that is what it takes.
OL,9,FHe feels it is him or them, and that
OL,10,Fis life in the Middle East. From his
OL,11,Fvantage point looking out ovre Israel,
OL,12,FLebanon and Syria, he hopes life will
OL,13,Fsoon look - and sound - quite
OL,14,Fdifferent.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
